          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>The unlikely mash-up of Mario and the adorable Rabbids from Rayman resulted in two fantastic Nintendo Switch strategy games, and for anyone looking to add them to their collection, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FKCXCHRP?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">check out the Amazon-exclusive double pack</a> before <a href="https://amzn.to/3KBuV5O" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Big Deal Days</a> ends. Released September 18 for $30, the double pack with Kingdom Battle and Sparks of Hope is now on sale for only $20. It's one of several <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/best-amazon-big-deal-days-ps5-and-nintendo-switch-game-deals/1100-6535295/" data-ref-id="1100-6535295">notable Nintendo Switch exclusives on sale for Big Deal Days</a>. For more Mario, check out Amazon's deal on <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mario-Vs-Donkey-KongTM-Nintendo-Switch/dp/B0CJ3DTSRD?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mario vs. Donkey Kong</a>.</p><div title="6533945 - Mario + Rabbids Double Pack Preorder" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="4100" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6533945 - Mario + Rabbids Double Pack Preorder" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FKCXCHRP?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0FKCXCHRP?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchant